                <title>They put Us far apart --  
</title>
            </titleStmt>
            <publicationStmt>
                <p>The Poems of Emily Dickinson, Johnson, 1955</p>
            </publicationStmt>
            <sourceDesc>
                <p>Emily Dickinson Archive</p>
            </sourceDesc>
        </fileDesc>
    </teiHeader>
    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J474">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>They put Us far apart --</l>
                    <l>As separate as Sea</l>
                    <l>And Her unsown Peninsula --</l>
                    <l>We signified "These see" --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>They took away our Eyes --</l>
                    <l>They thwarted Us with Guns --</l>
                    <l>"I see Thee" each responded straight</l>
                    <l>Through Telegraphic Signs --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>With Dungeons -- They devised --</l>
                    <l>But through their thickest skill --</l>
                    <l>And their opaquest Adamant --</l>
                    <l>Our Souls saw -- just as well --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>They summoned Us to die --</l>
                    <l>With sweet alacrity</l>
                    <l>We stood upon our stapled feet --</l>
                    <l>Condemned -- but just -- to see --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Permission to recant --</l>
                    <l>Permission to forget --</l>
                    <l>We turned our backs upon the Sun</l>
                    <l>For perjury of that --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Not Either -- noticed Death</l>
                    <l>Of Paradise -- aware --</l>
                    <l>Each other's Face -- was all the Disc</l>
                    <l>Each other's setting -- saw --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
        </body>
